  <name>Image Inpainter</name>
  <summary>Remove unwanted objects from images using AI-powered inpainting.</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
      Image Inpainter is a desktop application for removing unwanted objects from images using advanced AI techniques. It provides an easy-to-use interface for inpainting images with high accuracy.
      The application is designed for photographers, designers, and content creators who need to clean up images.
    </p>
    <p>
      Key features:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>AI-powered object removal and inpainting</li>
      <li>Batch processing multiple images</li>
      <li>User-friendly graphical interface</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      The tool is optimized for accuracy and speed on modern desktops and can be used
      entirely offline once installed.
    </p>
  </description>

